"title": "5951: slander",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5951",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>False and malicious talk about others. It not only harms those against whom it is directed, but also brings ruin to those who propagate it.</p>\n<h2>Slander condemned</h2>\n<h3>Slander is sinful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:21–7:23</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:19–15:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:4-Jer9:6\">JER 9:4–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:9\">EZK 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:29-Rom1:31\">ROM 1:29–1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:20\">2CO 12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:2-2Tim3:4\">2TI 3:2–3:4</a></p>\n<h3>Slander is forbidden</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:16\">LEV 19:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:1\">EXO 23:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:30\">PRO 3:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:18\">PRO 10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:22\">PRO 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:31\">EPH 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:8\">COL 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:3\">TIT 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1-Titus3:2\">TIT 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:11\">JAS 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1\">1PE 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>Slander is destructive</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:27\">PRO 16:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:9\">PRO 11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:28\">PRO 26:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:10\">PRO 30:10</a></p>\n<h2>Dealing with slander</h2>\n<h3>Committing one's cause to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps120:1-Ps120:2\">PSA 120:1–120:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:1-Ps12:7\">PSA 12:1–12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:14-Ps31:20\">PSA 31:14–31:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:1-Ps64:4\">PSA 64:1–64:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:6-Ps69:21\">PSA 69:6–69:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:1-Ps109:5\">PSA 109:1–109:5</a></p>\n<h3>Maintaining one's integrity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:23\">PSA 119:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:15\">1PE 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:9\">1PE 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15-1Pet3:17\">1PE 3:15–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Rejoicing in the Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">ACT 5:41</a></p>\n<h3>Not listening to slander</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:9\">1SA 24:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:4\">PRO 17:4</a></p>\n<h2>Judgment upon slanderers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:28\">PRO 21:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:13-Deut22:19\">DEU 22:13–22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:5\">PRO 19:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:9\">PRO 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:28\">PRO 21:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:20-Isa29:21\">ISA 29:20–29:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:7-Isa51:8\">ISA 51:7–51:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:10\">1CO 6:9–6:10</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of slander</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:18\">JER 18:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:7-Gen39:20\">GEN 39:7–39:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:1-1Kgs21:14\">1KI 21:1–21:14</a> <em>Naboth's vineyard</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:5-Neh6:7\">NEH 6:5–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:13\">PSA 31:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:15-Ps35:16\">PSA 35:15–35:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:19-Ps38:20\">PSA 38:19–38:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:5-Ps41:9\">PSA 41:5–41:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:2\">LUK 23:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:13-Acts6:14\">ACT 6:13–6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:5-Acts24:9\">ACT 24:5–24:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:8\">ROM 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:9-3John1:10\">3JN 1:9–1:10</a></p>",
